com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport

Class SecurityDimension

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport.SecurityDimension

  • public final class SecurityDimension
extends Object
    A dimension for security permissions in the security schema. Typical dimensions are things such as "Security Classification", "Compartment", or "Role".

    Each SecurityDimension specifies what the possible valid values are within that dimension.

    An individual security model will consist of one or more SecurityDimensions.

    1.0
